events.name: New York Knicks at Cleveland Cavaliers

headlines.description: — As the crowd's roar enveloped him, Kevin Love wrapped his arms around Darius Garland and thought back to those days when the Cavaliers were the biggest game in town.
headlines.shortLinkText: Love's barrage, Garland's 3 help Cavs hold off Knicks 95-93

events.name: Indiana Pacers at New Orleans Pelicans

headlines.description: — Devonte' Graham scored 25 points, Josh Hart had 22 points and 10 rebounds, and the New Orleans Pelicans defeated the Indiana Pacers 117-113 on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Graham, Valanciunas push Pelicans past Pacers, 117-113

events.name: Chicago Bulls at Oklahoma City Thunder

headlines.description: — Nicola Vucevic had 26 points and 15 rebounds, and the Chicago Bulls withstood a fierce rally by Oklahoma City to beat the Thunder 111-110 on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Vucevic, Bulls withstand late Thunder rally, win 111-110

headlines.description: — Chris Paul and his 36-year-old legs played 40 minutes of basketball for the Phoenix Suns on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Booker, Paul lead Suns past depleted Jazz, 115-109
